Packages
com.att.aro.commonui Contains reusable classes that provide UI components which are used throughout the ARO Data Analyzer application.
com.att.aro.images Contains an enumeration with methods used for identifying and retrieving Images and ImageIcons that are used throughout the ARO Data Analyzer application.
com.att.aro.main Main Package containing all UI classes.
com.att.aro.model Contains classes for parsing trace data, analyzing it, and containing the resulting data in bean classes so that the ARO Data Analyzer can display it.
com.att.aro.pcap Package containing different types of packet bean and adapter classes.
com.att.aro.video Contains a class that provides a Video player in the ARO Data Analyzer.
com.att.aro.videocapture Provides classes for capturing video from the Android Emulator while collecting application trace data.
